      Product description

      Mixed packs of delicious wet food for cats, in a variety of gluten-free and protein-rich flavours, made with pure natural ingredients for essential nutrients and beneficial omega-3 fatty acids.

      Encore Cans in Broth Saver Pack 24 x 70g is a high-quality wet food for cats, made with natural ingredients and a high meat- or fish content. It is gluten-free and contains no preservatives, which can make this food appealing to nutritionally-conscious cat owners. The protein-rich food can help to support your cat's lean muscle mass, acting as the ideal supplement to dry food.
      Not only is this Encore Cans in Broth Saver Pack 24 x 70g wet food particularly tasty, it is also a source of beneficial omega-3 fatty acids, which can help to promote healthy skin and a glossy coat. The high moisture content of this dish can help to support sufficient fluid intake. As this food is gluten-free, it is easy to digest and the perfect choice for cats with more sensitive stomachs.

      Encore Cans in Broth Saver Pack 24 x 70g at a glance:
      • High-quality wet food for cats
      • Recipe with 100% natural ingredient: no preservatives
      • High meat- or fish content: provides plenty of protein
      • Gluten-free: also suitable for cats with a sensitive stomach
      • Omega-3 fatty acids: can keep skin healthy and coat glossy
      • High moisture content: to support sufficient fluid intake in cats that struggle to drink enough water
      • Designed as a supplementary food: can be served with dry food
      • Saver Pack: for stocking up and saving
      The Chicken Selection contains the following flavour varieties:
      • 5 x 70g Chicken Breast
      • 4 x 70g Chicken Breast & Cheese
      • 3 x 70g Chicken Breast with Ham
      The Fish Selection contains the following flavour varieties:
      • 5 x 70g Tuna with Shrimp
      • 4 x 70g Ocean Fish
      • 3 x 70g Sardine with Tuna Fillet
      The Finest Selection contains the following flavour varieties:
      • 2 x 70g Tuna with Shrimp
      • 2 x 70g Ocean Fish
      • 2 x 70g Sardine with Tuna Fillet
      • 2 x 70g Chicken Breast
      • 2 x 70g Chicken Breast & Cheese
      • 2 x 70g Chicken Breast with Ham

      Privacy Preference Centre

      When you visit a website, it may retrieve or store data about your browser. This usually takes the form of cookies. This can be data about you, your settings or your device. In most cases, the data is used to ensure that the website is functioning as expected. This data cannot normally identify you personally. However, it can provide you with a more personalised web experience. As we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow certain types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking certain types of cookies may result in a compromised experience with the website and services we provide.
      Further information

      Manage Consent Preferences

      Strictly Necessary Cookies

      Always Active

      These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

      Performance Cookies

      These cookies allow us to count visits and traffic sources so we can measure and improve the performance of our site. They help us to know which pages are the most and least popular and see how visitors move around the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. If you do not allow these cookies we will not know when you have visited our site, and will not be able to monitor its performance.

      Functional Cookies

      These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages.    If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.

      Targeting Cookies

      These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.

      External advertising partners - Customer list

      We use special mechanisms to address our users and customers with advertising. Existing profiles of our advertising partners are matched using (hashed) email addresses (so-called customer lists), which enables a targeted approach using interest-based adverts.
